{
  "id": "adv_card_szk_52_03",
  "title": "兵藤雫 3話 嬉し過ぎて昇天しそう",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "まさか雫がスタッフに連れて行かれるなんて……\n早く助けに行かないと……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t believe Shizuku is being taken away by staff…\nI need to hurry and help her…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "ただいま……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m back…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 166.6666666999994,
          "startTime": 6.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "雫！　良かった、無事だったんだな\n外に連れ出されて、一体何があったんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku! Thank goodness‚ you’re safe.\nYou were taken outside—what on earth happened?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "何が起こったのか、自分でも分からない……\nとにかく、起こったことをありのまま話すと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t even know what happened myself…\nAnyway‚ if I just tell it as it happened…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "ファンですって言われた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was told‚ “I’m your fan.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.4333318074
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　スタッフの中に雫のファンがいたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh? There was a staff member who was your fan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.4333318074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "違う……案内されてステージの裏に行ったら\nさあたんが……私の推しが、いて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No… when I was guided backstage—\nSaa-tan… my oshi… was there…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.8191686063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.8999984741
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "目をキラキラさせて……雫ちゃんのファンです\n握手して下さいって言われた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With sparkling eyes‚ she said‚ “I’m your fan‚ Shizuku-chan.”\n\"Please shake hands with me…\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.8666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.6999984741
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "その後、さあたんにお願いされて\nツーショットチェキを撮って、サインしてきた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After that‚ at her request‚\nwe took a two-shot polaroid‚ and I signed it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.6333318074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして……これは夢……？\n私、夢見てる……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Could this… be a dream…?\nAm I dreaming…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.2333318074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.2999984741
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "お互いがお互いのファンだった訳か\nそれは、なんというか……貴重な体験だったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you were both each other’s fans.\nWell‚ that’s… a rare experience.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.5999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、推しと交流出来て良かったじゃないか\n実際に会ってみてどうだった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ it’s great that you got to interact with your oshi.\nHow was it actually meeting her?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.0999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.3666651408
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "可愛かった……！　ステージではあんなに\nかっこいいのに本人ははんなりゆったりした雰囲気で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She was so cute…! On stage she’s so cool‚\nbut in person she had this gentle‚ laid-back aura…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.0999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "あの声と雰囲気で「雫はん」って言われると\nドキドキする……京都弁は可愛いの暴力……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When she said “Shizuku-han” in that voice and mood…\nMy heart pounded… Kyoto dialect is violently cute…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.2999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.7333368937
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……推しが尊過ぎて辛い……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… my oshi is too precious‚ it hurts…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.7333368937,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.666670227
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、雫が無事で良かったよ\n……ん？　なんだか物販の方が騒がしくなってきたな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I’m just glad you’re safe.\n…Hm? The merch area’s getting noisy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.8999984741,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2333.328247099999,
          "startTime": 94.9999984741
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "多分、もうすぐチェキ会が始まるから……\n行列に並んでるファンがそわそわして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Probably because the polaroid event is about to start…\nThe fans waiting in line are getting restless…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.8999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.7000030517
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "……はっ！　推しとのツーショットチェキ……\n私も行かなきゃ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah! A two-shot polaroid with my oshi…\nI have to go too…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.2838587037,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "写真なら、さっき裏で一緒に撮ったんじゃないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But didn’t you just take one backstage?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.0000030517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "それはさあたんの分……私の分の写真は撮ってない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was for Saa-tan… I didn’t take one for myself…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.7000030517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.7000030517
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4の肩書きを利用して、アイドルに\nチェキを求めるのは……私のポリシーに反する……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Using my BIG4 title to ask an idol—\nfor a polaroid… goes against my policy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.5476220993,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.333336385
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03-szk015.m4a",
      "text": "ファンとしてチケット代は自腹で払う……\nチェキ券をちゃんと買って、並んで、写真を撮る……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As a fan‚ I’ll pay for the ticket out of my own pocket…\nI’ll buy a polaroid ticket‚ line up‚ and take the photo properly…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.1666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.9000030517
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "謙虚で、マナーを守る、ドルオタの鑑……\nBIG4になっても雫は変わらないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Humble and respectful—a model idol fan…\nEven after becoming BIG4‚ Shizuku hasn’t changed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.1666651408,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1533.3302816000014,
          "startTime": 133.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.3999984741
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_03-szk016.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、見て……\nツーショットチェキに直筆のメッセージで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ look…\nOn the two-shot polaroid‚ with a handwritten message…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.3666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
