      "text": "私も、凄く嬉しい……\n忘れられない特別な日になった……ありがとう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m really happy too…\nIt’s become an unforgettable‚ special day… thank you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.3666651408,
      "sfxList": []
