      "text": "じゃあ、そろそろ旅館に戻ろうか\nきっとみんなも雫の帰りを待ってるぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ let’s head back to the inn.\nI’m sure everyone else is waiting for you too.",
        "id": ""
